{
  "id": "email-work",
  "name": "工作邮件",
  "category": "email",
  "description": "一封正式的工作邮件，带有专业的格式和签名",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.04,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "setting",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "职场|公司|办公室|工作",
        "description": "职场相关场景可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "date": {
      "type": "date",
      "format": "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm",
      "description": "邮件日期时间"
    },
    "subject": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "邮件主题"
    },
    "sender": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "发件人名称"
    },
    "senderInitial": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "发件人首字母"
    },
    "senderTitle": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "发件人职位"
    },
    "recipient": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "收件人名称"
    },
    "greeting": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "邮件问候语"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 500,
      "description": "邮件正文内容"
    },
    "contactInfo": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "联系方式"
    },
    "priority": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "普通",
      "options": ["紧急", "重要", "普通"],
      "description": "邮件优先级"
    },
    "attachments": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "无附件",
      "description": "附件信息"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一封工作邮件的内容。\n\n背景信息：\n- 发件人：{{sender}}（{{senderTitle}}）\n- 收件人：{{recipient}}\n- 邮件主题：{{subject}}\n- 场景：{{scene}}\n\n要求：\n1. 内容专业正式，符合职场礼仪\n2. 语气要符合发件人的职位和性格\n3. 结构清晰，有问候、正文、结尾\n4. 字数控制在200-400字之间\n5. 可以包含工作相关的事项\n\n请直接输出邮件内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "professional",
    "colors": ["#667eea", "#764ba2", "#fafafa"],
    "mood": "正式专业"
  },
  "rarity": "common",
  "collectible": true
}